headline: 3 Truck Stocks to Keep an Eye on Despite Industry Hiccups
summary: The Zacks Industry Rank for the Transportation-Truck industry paints a dull picture mainly due to the slowdown in freight demand. We believe stocks like JBHT, SAIA and KNX are better positioned to escape industry challenges presently.
